[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]]國防軍與納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫防衛軍於2016年4月2日與[[亞塞拜然|亞塞拜然]]國防軍就[[納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫|納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫]]地區爭議爆發衝突。一天後，亞塞拜然國防部宣布單方面停火，但據納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫防衛軍消息，攻擊仍持續<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://nkrmil.am/main/en/newsMore1248.html|title=NKR Defence Ministry’s Statement|date=|last=|first=|publisher=NKRmil.am|website=|access-date=}}</ref>。衝突雙方官方聲明顯示，18名亞美尼亞及12名亞塞拜然士兵於衝突中死亡<ref name="kp">{{Cite web|url=http://www.kp.ru/online/news/2353276/|title=Минобороны Азербайджана: Перестрелка в Карабахе прекратилась|accessdate=2 April 2016|date=2 April 2016|work=[[Komsomolskaya_Pravda|Komsomolskaya Pravda]]|language=ru|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127100715/https://www.kp.ru/online/news/2353276/}}</ref>，另有雙方均損失少數軍事設備。[[聯合國人道事務協調廳|聯合國人道事務協調廳]]確認三名平民死亡<ref name="ocha">{{Cite web|url=http://reliefweb.int/report/azerbaijan/nagorno-karabakh-conflict-situation-report-no-1-03-apr-2016|title=Nagorno-Karabakh Conflict Situation Report No. 1 (as of 03 Apr 2016)|accessdate=4 April 2016|date=3 April 2016|publisher=[[ReliefWeb|ReliefWeb]]|archive-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404094513/http://reliefweb.int/report/azerbaijan/nagorno-karabakh-conflict-situation-report-no-1-03-apr-2016}}</ref>。雙方於4月5日達成停火協議，並於當地時間12時生效<ref name="casualties">{{cite web|url=http://www.mod.gov.az/index2.php?content=news/2016/20160405_melumat|title=Information|publisher=Ministry of Defense of Azerbaijan|date=5 April 2016|accessdate=5 April 2016|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410073030/http://mod.gov.az/index2.php?content=news%2F2016%2F20160405_melumat|archivedate=2016年4月10日}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/209646/|title=Karabakh parties agree on bilateral ceasefire starting Apr 5 midday|date=5 April 2016|work=PanARMENIAN.Net|accessdate=2016-04-07|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408072332/http://www.panarmenian.net/eng/news/209646|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞美尼亞少將表示亞塞拜然軍隊成功的偵查及壓力測試，而完成其初步目標<ref>{{cite web|url=http://daytube.az/videos/24064/|title=Армянский генерал: «Азербайджанская армия выполнила все поставленные задачи»|work=DayTube|accessdate=2016-04-07|archive-date=2016-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412142937/http://daytube.az/videos/24064/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==背景==
[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫共和国|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫共和国]]事實上獨立於亞塞拜然，但其領土於國際上多承認為亞塞拜然的一部份<ref>{{cite web| url =http://www.un.org/press/en/2008/ga10693.doc.htm| title =General Assembly adopts resolution reaffirming territorial integrity of Azerbaijan, demanding withdrawal of all Armenian forces| publisher =United Nations| date =14 March 2008| accessdate =30 Aug 2015| archive-date =2019-03-25| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190325020542/https://www.un.org/press/en/2008/ga10693.doc.htm| dead-url =no}}</ref>。自1994年[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]結束後，基於{{link-en|比什凱克協議|Bishkek Protocol}}的停火生效，而此次衝突為自1994年來違反該協議最嚴重之行為<ref name="ocha"/>。

